definitions.definition: A small village and civil parish in Tewkesbury borough , Gloucestershire , England ( OS grid ref SO8925 ) .
A civil parish in West Northamptonshire district, Northamptonshire , England , previously in South Northamptonshire district.
A town and shire , the Shire of Boddington , in the Peel region of Western Australia .
